  <a name="departmentpennant"></a>
	<dt style="font-weight: bold">DEPARTMENT PENNANT</dt>
  <dd>See &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvs2.html#servicepennant">service pennant</a>&rsquo;.
  <p>
